    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find for any enthusiast or collector. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine and not a single chip or scratch to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery still firm and smelling fresh, and every electronic component functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is impeccable, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and stored in a climate-controlled garage. You can expect a driving experience that is indistinguishable from a brand-new vehicle.",
