      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and sustained aesthetic appeal. Featuring a documented service history and a well-preserved interior, it offers a refined driving experience for the discerning professional. Available now for immediate acquisition.",
