    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me and is still in really solid shape, ready for all your upcoming adventures! It drives smoothly and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice if you're looking for something dependable without the brand-new price tag. I'm super excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
